text: Ordered thru Grab. Rice was missing. Chicken was so dry and small. Burger steak looks so pale.

Orders are always missing. Honestly,  one of the worst food chain for online delivery.

Missing burger. A missing bloody burger for goodness sake!!!!!!
Ordered Grab delivery. All orders were correct, with no missing items. The bags were taped to prevent any discrepancy. All food were nicely packed. Thank you very much. Keep up the good work.

Ordered via Grab but rider said order was taken by someone else at the restaurant?? Judging by the other reviews I’m not the only one having problems with missing orders. The management needs to do something about this…
Look at the burger, not even a slice of onion.  No fries, they just give pringles.
